Privacy Policy for Fluxo
Last updated: March 2026

Fluxo respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how information is collected and used within the app.

Information We Collect

When you create an account, we collect your email address for authentication and account management purposes.

We also collect user-generated content such as training sessions, templates, and related fitness data to provide the core functionality of the app.

How We Use Your Information

Your data is used solely to:

• Provide account authentication
• Store and display your training information
• Enable app functionality
• Maintain security and prevent abuse

We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for advertising purposes.

Data Storage

All data is securely stored using Supabase infrastructure. Data is associated with your account and accessible only to you.

Tracking and Advertising

Fluxo does not use third-party advertising and does not track users across apps or websites.

Your Rights

You may request deletion of your account and associated data at any time by contacting us.

